Package: arplsbaseline
Type: Package
Title: Baseline Correction using the ARPLS Method
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-09-23
Author: Jessica Sam
Maintainer: Jessica Sam <jessica-sam@outlook.co.nz>
Description: This package will calculate a baseline to data using  
  Asymmetrically Reweighted Penalised Least Squares Smoothing and correct data
  according to this baseline. A Spectrum object is created after using the main 
  baseline function and methods that can be called.
